hopobject.body: magic story very thanks burn slim price Shain Gandee, the 21-year-old star of MTV's show "Buckwild," was found dead on April 1, 2013 in West Virginia, TMZ reports. In what appeared to be a car accident, authorities said Gandee was found, along with two other bodies, in a vehicle 31 hours after he was reported missing. The raucous MTV show characterizes the "wild" lifestyle of a group of teenagers living in West Virginia. The show, which follows the format of success "Jersey Shore," focuses on the group of friends partying and performing several reckless stunts for fun.
